# Real data — never committed to this public repo (see "Self-hosted usage" in README.md):
config.sh
memory/
scripts/local/
.claude/settings.local.json

# projects/ and Business/ keep their top-level folder + README tracked (so a fresh clone has
# both ready to populate), but their real contents (repo checkouts, client data) stay private:
projects/*
!projects/README.md
Business/*
!Business/README.md
